Aɣerbaz gar zik d tura.
Mebla ccek, aɣerbaz d aɣbalu amenzu n ddunit ideg amdan, akken yebɣu yili uẓayer-ines, d argaz neɣ d tameṭṭut, d aẓawali neɣ d amerkanti, d aberkan neɣ d acebḥan… yessefk ad d-iɛeddi fell-as, ad d-yagem timussniwin, yis-sent ad yezger talsa, ad yessiweḍ ayen i d-yegmer d wayen yessen ɣer tsuta i d-yettasen d win ur nessin ara, akka i iteddu wakud.
Aɣerbaz d aḥric am waṭas n yiḥricen deg tudert n umdan, ɣur-s talliyin, yal yiwet s tulmisin-is, s wacu i d-tufrar, d acu i d amaynut i swayes i d-tegla yal tallit, dacu i d-yerna win yellan fell-as d amasay amenzu (aneɣlaf n usedwel).
Deg tmurt-nneɣ, acḥal n yineɣlafen i d-iɛeddan ɣef uqerru n teɣlift n usegmi, segmi i d-tḥella timmunent di 62.
Yal yiwen d acu i d-yefka, amek yessuddes aɣerbaz azzayri d wanti tiktiwin i swayes i d-yegla.
Asteqsi iɣef nettnadi tiririt ass-a, d amgired yellan gar uɣerbaz n zik d win n wass-a.
Wissen ma yuẓa neɣ yuɣal ɣer deffir neɣ akken kan i yeqqim.
D ameslay i nsel qrib yal ass ɣef wuguren, ulac win tezgel tyita.
Bdu s yinelmaden d yimawlan-nsen, ttcetkayen, qqaren arraw-nneɣ ur gezzun ara.
Kif kif ula d iselmaden, qqaren bezzaf ẓẓayet fell-aɣ teɛkemt.
Inemhalen seg tma-nsen, imaswaḍen d twacult akk n uɣerbaz, yal wa s umur-is n usenqed d ucetki.
Maca, tifrat anida-tt ?
Ma nruḥ ɣer yimasayen (inemhalen n usedwel), yal wa s ṛṛay-is d wanta tamacahut ara d-yawi !
Anelmad yeqqar i yimawlan-is.
Amgarad amenzwaru, a-t-an deg uxemmem d uqerruy n uqcic s timmad-is, acku d netta i d aɣbalu amezwaru i terza temsalt.
Maca axemmem-a, lqay, ɣur-s geddac ifurkawen i d-yekkan seg tudert n yal ass, i d-yeffɣen seg tmetti ideg yettidir uqcic ass-a.
Zik, aqcic, yeqqar i yiman-is akken ad yerbeḥ ikayaden-is, ur as-fkan ara tallelt yimawlan-is, acku ur stufan ara, wa tecɣeb-it ddunit, wa yettazzal deffir n uɣrum.
Imawlan, zgan qqaren yiwen n wawal i tarwa-nsen: Ma teɣram i kunwi, d kunwi ara iɣelten.
Maca tura, tayemmat, tezga teqqar i mmi-s: Ḥrec, ɣer, ma trebḥeḍ akayad-ik, tettalaseḍ aglawal d warrazen-nniḍen.
d ayen i yeǧǧan aqcic ass-a, yeqqar i yimawlan-is mačči i netta.
Tugar tawant.
Imdanen zik, d iẓawaliyen, tuget ur ṛwin ara aɣrum, ur tugar ara tawant.
Ɣef waya, aqcic yesɛa kan yiwen n umrig, yis-s i yekkat, yis-s i yettqabal taswiɛt.
Amrig-a, d taɣuri, imi ur yestufa ara ad yeg ayen-nniḍen.
Deg uɣerbaz, iban, ma deg berra, ulac allalen n wurar yellan ass-a.
Leqraya, tuɣal-as d tannumi.
Arrac n tura, ufan-d tugar tawant deg tmetti, ixxamen wessiɛen, uraren yemgaraden, tuččit yelhan.
Ayagi yak, yessettuy-asen leqraya, ur as-fkin ara azal-is ma nesserwes-itt ɣer wallalen yugten.
Ɣur waṭas n yinelmaden n tura, aɣerbaz d zzyada, d asezri n wakud, ɣas ur yeɣri ara, llan yimawlan-is ad t-allen, ad as-fken ayen iwumi yesra.
Taččart n wahil.
Ma nesserwes ahil n uɣerbaz amenzu gar tmurt-nneɣ d kra n tmura yuẓan, ad d-naf amgared meqqren.
Amedya ;
Deg tmurt n Japon, anelmad segmi ara yekcem deg uswir amenzu alamma d wis kraḍ, ad yettɛedday war ikayaden, acku iswi d almad yesɛan adda.
Maca ma nerra lwelha ɣer wahil n uɣebaz amenzu ɣur-neɣ, ad naf, amedya deg uswir wis ukkuẓ, anelmad yeqqar ilmuden ẓẓayen ɣef uswir-is am umezruy, tarakalt, tasreḍt d tussna… Annect-a, bla ma nettu taččart n wahil d temɣer n yidlisen iɣurbizen.
Aselmad iɛerreḍ ad yekfu ahil, acku amaswaḍ yettabaɛ-it s deffir, imi ula d aneggaru-a, ɣur-s isuḍaf swayes ixeddem.
Din i tt-yettaɣ unelmad, imi ur igezzu ula aḥric amecṭuḥ seg wayen yeqqar d wayen yettaru.
Zik, ahil yellan deg walmuden fessus, yal almud yettas-d i lmend n uswir d tzemmar n unelmad.
Acku deg uɣerbaz amenzu ladɣa, anelmad yesra ad yissin amek ara yaru, ad yemmeslay, u ad yissin ad yeḥseb.
Ma d ilmuden n tussna, alamma yuli ɣer yiswiren ufella ara yejbu fell-asen.
Aẓayer n uselmad.
Aselmad di tallit-nni yezrin, ɣur-s azal.
Ma nesla i yisem-is, igellu-d s lhiba, yettuqader deg uɣerbaz neɣ di berra.
Ula d inelmaden ttkukrun ad t-mmaggren di berra.
Maca, aselmad n wass-a, yettujerred seg kra n yizerfan.
Ur yesɛi ara aẓayer-nni n zik, acku isuḍaf imaynuten i d-yeffɣen, fkan aṭas n uzref i unelmad daxel n tneɣrit.
Tettwagdel tyita, ahat ilaq waya, imi tikwal tettḍurru.
Maca akken ad yettwagdel ɣef uselmad ula d asuɣu s uwellih ɣef unelmad ara ixedmen tabannaḍt, ayagi yerna tilelli i yinelmaden ad beɛden acemma ɣef ulmud.
War ma nettu zzkara n kra n yimawlan d leḥris i xeddmen ɣef uselmad, ma yella tarwa-nsen ur d-tufrar ara.
Tigi yak, sneɣsent seg yiseɣ-nni i ila uselmad akken ad yili d tigejdit ireṣṣan i uselḥu n uɣerbaz ɣer sdat.
Aya iɣef i d-nenna ɣef tuɣalin n uẓayer n uselmad ɣer deffir, ur aɣ-yettagi ara ad d-nini belli llan kra n yiselmaden ur nxeddem ara amahil-nsen akken ilaq, ceɣben-ten lecɣal-nniḍen ɛlaḥsab n tmussni n unelmad.
Timental-a akk yezwaren, mlalent-d, gant tagruma n wuguren i yesneqsen deg wazal n uɣerbaz azzayri.
Ɣas ma gtent temcukkal, ur d-yewwi ara ad nenker kra n wayen yuqmen, iteddun deg ubrid n tidet.
Ar taggara, ad d-nini ulac am ṣṣfa deg umahil, aselmad ad yeqdec s wul-is d leḥmala.
Ula d imawlan, sɛan azal deg waya, yewwi-d ad weṣṣin tarwa ɣer leḥmala n tɣuri d uqader n uɣerbaz.
Imasayen seg tama-nsen, ilaq ad xedmen ayen igerrzen i tilin n uɣerbaz deg ubrid-is.
Ahat yiwen wass, ad yifrir, ad yeṭṭef adeg seg wid ifazen.
Khaled Achoui.
Cwiṭ seg tmucuha n leqbayel.
Amcic d uγerda.
Qqaren, yella yiwen n umcic akken kan yebda yetturar d ameẓyan, yemlal-d d uγerda d tanudda-s neγ (tizya-s).
Tturaren Seg wakken myeεǧaben, ihi tturaren si ṣṣbeḥ ar tmeddit.
Yenna-as umcic: “Ihi i imi nemsefham, azekka ad nemlil ad nurar daγen am wass-a yak?
”.
Aγerda, yerra-as: “Ih, azekka taṣebḥit ad nemlil”.
Mi yekcem uγerda s axxam-nsen, yenṭeq baba-s γur-s: ”Anida teddiḍ si ṣṣbeḥ ar tura?
”.
Aγerda: “Annaγ a baba, lliγ tturareγ d yiwen umeddakkel-iw amzun-it”.
-Isem-is umedakel-agi inek?
-Isem-is ah…amcic.
Dγa baba-s, tbeddel ṣṣifa-s: “Annaγ ad ak-yexdeε Rebbi, qṛib temeččeḍ ur ẓriγ”.
Yemma-s, texlaε akken-nniḍen: ”Yak a mmi, imcac d iεdawen-nneγ, ur aγ-ḥemmlen ara i tdukli.
Lemmer ad aγ-ṭṭfen, ad aγ-ččen”.
Aγerda: “Semmeḥ-iyi a baba, semmeḥ-iyi a yemma, dayen ur ttεawadeγ ad uγaleγ, cwi kan selkeγ ».
Si tama-nniḍen, amcic mi yewweḍ γer uxxam-nsen, yesteqsa-t baba-s: “Anida teddiḍ si ṣṣbeḥ ay amcic a mmi?
”.
Amcic: “A baba, lliγ zehhuγ d yiwen uḥbib-iw”.
Baba-s: “Isem-is uḥbib-ik?
”.
Amcic: “Isem-is ah…aγerda”.
Dγa tsuγ yemma-s wala baba-s: “Anwa anwa?
”.
Amcic: “Aγerda ayγer?
Acimi?
”.
Baba-s: “Annaγ ay ameslub, lemmer teḥriceḍ, ad t-id-teṭṭfeḍ i wakken ad t-nečč, yak iγerdayen d ikeryen-nneγ”.
Amcic: “Semmeḥ-iyi a baba, nekk d amecṭuḥ ur ssineγ ara, maca azekka ad d-yuγal i wakken ad yurar yid-i, ad t-id-ṭṭfeγ, ad t-nečč”.
Azekka-nni tafejrit, yeqsed umcic s axxam, yessawel-as: “Ay aγerda, ay aγerda”.
Aγerda: “Anwa akka?
Acu tebγiḍ?
”.
-Nekk d aḥbib-ik, ffeγ-d ad nurar.
-Ala, ur tturareγ ara.
-Acimi?
-Ayen akken i ak-yenna baba-k leεca, yenna-yi-t-id ula d nekk baba.
Yahia Yanes.
Tuddsa tagraɣlant i uḥraz n ugama.
Ḥeḍru-d ad negren yiɣersiwen-a!
Deg yiwen n yisalli i d-tessuffeɣ Tuddsa tagraɣlant i uḥraz n ugama, yedda-d kra n umḍan n yiɣersiwen, n umenẓaw n Tferka (Tafriqt) abeɛda, i yellan ɣef yimi n nnger.
Nezmer ad d-nebder seg yiɣersiwen-a Izem, Ilu, Aḍebɛiw, Aɣerwaṭ (arinusirus), amdeɣ (girafe) d wuccen n lexla.
I tifrat n kra seg wugur-a, txelles Teseqqamut Turufant yiwen n wahil, s wazal n 12 n yimelyan iyuruten, ara yeǧǧen imezdaɣ idiganen ad zdin tamnaḍt n tudert akked yiɣersiwen imehhazen (prédateurs) war ma yenṭer yiwen seg-sen.
Deg wahil-a, ara yettwaselḥun sɣur SOS, ad naf iswi amenzu d aseḥbes ulamma cwiṭ n tmettant n yizmawen, iɣilasen, iḍebɛiwen, iḍan n lexla d wuccanen ityupyanen, i simmal ttenṭerrayen seg useyyed berra i usaḍuf, annerni n tnezduɣin d ukcam n yimdanen di tẓegwa.
S tedrimt-a n Teseqqamut turufant, yezmer ad d-yawi kra n ubaɣur usenfar-a n uḥraz iwumi fkan azwel SOS Tiẓgi taferkant.
Ula d tiɣri i usumer n walbaɛḍ n yisenfaren-nniḍen, tettwaceyyeɛ i kra n tuddsiwin n tmetti tadigant.
Dɣa, iberreḥ-d s tumert-is unmazul n unemhal n wahil n Tuddsa tagraɣlant i uḥraz n ugama, seld tallelt-a s tedrimt n Teseqqamut turufant.
Yenna-d daɣen yesɛa ayendin d azal wahil-a, meskud ad yallel aɣersiw ad yesnerni azbu-is, ad d-yesnulfu i yiman-is tabaɣurt s wayen i as-d-yefka yakan ugama-is.
Ɣef wawal-is, ad yekki daɣ wahil-a deg uḥraz d usellek n kra n yiɣersiwen imehhazen n Tferka i iteddun ad negren, am nutni am yiɣersiwen igemrawen (proie).
Akkin i usenfar-a, yewwi-d ad d-nesmekti d akken, ɣas ma tikwal yesmurrus wahil n uḥraz i d-yettwaskarayen deg Tferka, mazal nnger yeṭṭafar ddeqs n yisenfan n yiɣersiwen, armi drus i d-yeqqimen seg-sen.
Amedya n yizem (Panthera leo) i yellan deg wumuɣ aẓewwaɣ deg umaḍal merra, akken i d-tewwi tuddsa-a tagraɣlant i uḥraz n ugama.
Talɣuɣa n ddunit n Kempo n tmurt n Sepenyul.
Tḥella-d 50 n cciɛat terbaεt taɣelnawt n Lezzayer.
Tewwi-d terbaεt n waddal n Kempo n tmurt n Lezzayer amḍiq wis kraḍ (03) deg tezrigt tis 16 n telɣuɣa n ddunit n tmurt n Sepenyul, i d-yellan seg 25 ar 27 seg waggur n yebrir 2019, anda i d(tḥella terbaεt taɣelnawt 50 n cciεat.
Gar-asent, 11 n wuraɣ, 22 n cciεat n teẓruft d 17 n cciεat n udrenz, deg yiwet n temsizzelt anda ttekkant 33 n tmura n ddunit.
Tikkelt-agi, turar terbaεt taɣelnawt s yilmeẓyen yesεan ddaw 21 n yiseggassen, yecban Malak Day Touba (19 n yesgassen), i d-yewwin snat (02) n cciεat n wuraɣ, deg taggayt n semi-Kempo d Full-Kempo.
Sḥassfen aṭas yimḍebbren n terbaεt n yinaddalel seg maḥyaf yessemres unefray n yiwet n temlilit, i yekksen cciεa n wuraɣ i unaddal Fayçal Chennah.
Tettekka tmurt n Lezzayer deg temsizzelt-agi s 19 n yinaddalen, s tlawin d yirgazen, deg taggayin yemgaraden n waddal n Kempo, anda qesden ad d-ḥellin amur ameqqran n cciεat deg talɣuɣa-agi, wa ad d-ilin deg yimeḍqan imezwura deg umyezwar n temsizzelt.
Ali Zalouk.
Bgayet.
Isallen n Uḥuddu aɣarim.
Ḍḥan-d yisehwa n yiberdan, d tamentilt n tmettant tamezwarut di tmurt-a, imi simmal zerrin yiseggasen, simmal yettimɣuṛ umḍan n wid yettmettaten s yisehwa.
Dɣa, deg yiḍ n 29/30 yebrir yezrin ɣef 03:53 n tnezzayt, iqeddacen n Uḥuddu aɣarim, seld asiwel n yiwen n umdan i asen-d-yessutren ad ruḥen s tazzla i tlemmast n temdint n Ticci, anda i yeḍṛa usegwu-a, uzzlen s uɣiwel ɣeṛ umḍiq-nni.
Lameεna imi leḥqen, ufan amdan-nni yewweḍ leεfu n Rebbi, wagi d yiwen n yilemẓi i yesεan 31 n yiseggasen seg tdayṛa n Uweqqas, daymi i yettwawi srid ɣer sbiṭaṛ-nsen.
Seg tama tayeḍ, deg yiwen n wass, 30-04-2019 ɣef 17:42 n tmeddit, tettwaddhem yiwet n teqcict n tmeẓṛit, deg umḍiq iwumi qqaṛen Tizi n Lexmis, sɣur yiwet n tkeṛṛust.
Taqcict-a, tesεa ala 4 n yiseggasen di leεmeṛ-is, dɣa temmut imir-n.
Ma yella d win i igan taluft, yerwel srid.
Tafekka n teqcict-a, tettwawi ɣer sbiṭaṛ n Sidi Ɛic, sɣur yiqeddacen n Uhuddu aɣarim.
Am wakken i aɣ-d-leḥqen yisallen sɣur-sen, d akken gren-d iman-nsen ula ass n sed 01-05 iεeddan deg yilel n « AIGUADE » di Bgayet, imi wwḍen-asen-d yisallen belli yeɣreq yiwen n yilemẓi dinna.
Imi leḥqen, iqeddacen-nsen sergen-t-id seg waman.
Dɣa, seld tasestant i xedmen, ufan-t d yiwen n usdawan seg Tɣerdayt i d-yusan akked d yemdukkal-is i wakken ad ḥewwsen.
Wagi d Mass ( H.
) i yesεan 21 n yiseggasen, i yettwawin i sbiṭaṛ n Bgayet.
Ad d-nesmekti belli, amḍan n yisehwa n yiberdan deg wayyur n yebrir 2019, yewweḍ ar 123, deg-s mmuten 08 n yimdanen, jeṛḥen 167.
Ma yella seg tazwara n 2019 ar ass-a, ḍṛan 526 n yisehwa, anda i mmuten 19 n yimdanen, u 616 nniḍen d imejṛaḥ.
Buzgan.
Tettcektay tddukkla Tiɛwinin.
Deg yiwen n wulɣu i d-tesuffeɣ i uzayez d tɣamsa, tettcektay tddukkla tadelsant Tiɛwinin, n tɣiwant n Buzgan, seg usewḥel n taggazt-is (subvention) sɣur yimḍebbren n twilayt.
Dɣa, gar wayen tqeddec deg unnar adelsan, d timlilit taseklant i d-tettheggi tddukkla i ihewwlen kra n yimḍebbren n twilayt n Tizi Uzzu, ɣef wawal n wid i d-yuran ulɣu.
Imi, ma nesmektay-d kan, ḥawla n tikkal i d-berrḥen yimheggiyen n teɣlust taseklant ɣef yiɛewwiqen i as-d-xeddment kra n tamiwin, gar-asent tadayra n Buzgan.
Akken i d-yewwi uberriḥ, iban-d tettwasewḥel tedrimt sɣur tedbelt n twilayt n Tizi Uzzu i yugin, s ubrid n Tenmehla n tedbelt tadigant (DAL), ad d-tserreḥ i tedrimt-nni i d-yefka Useqqamu aɣerfan awilay (APW) n Tizi Uzzu.
Seg yiwet n tama, ɣef wawal n yiɛeggalen n tddukkla, yella yenna-asen-d unemhal n tedbelt tadigant (DAL) d akken ilaq ɣef uselway n tddukkla Tiɛwinin ad yerzu ɣer uxxam n tɣellist n Tizi Uzzu akken ad d-serrḥen i tedrimt-nni.
Ɣef rray amatu, acewwel n tddukkla-a sɣur yimḍebbren icudd ɣer warmuden-is idelsanen, tugart timlilit taseklant, ur nehwi i kra.
Aṭas n tikkal, yuɣ lḥal, i tegguma tdayra ad tefk ttesriḥ i yiɛeggalen akken ad suddsen di talwit asarag-nsen.
Qqaren-d yiɛeggalen, segmi tebda teɣlust taseklant, tessewɛar-asen tedbelt tilufa.
Rnu, ur bɣin yimasayen mi d-kkaten wat Tiɛwinin deg yiqeddacen n « Drag » n « Dal ».
Ulamma ulac tadrimt, teḥres akka tegnit ɣef tddukkla-a tilemẓit i d-ilulen deg useggas n 2013, ur heggan yiɛeggalen-is ad brun i ṭṭbel deg waman, d warmuden akk i d-ssuddusen teɣzi n useggas, am yisaragen, amezgun, tazabut s teqbaylit, d usfuggel n yimulliyen imezrayen neɣ idelsanen.
D aya i yeǧǧan dɣa Tiddukkla Tiɛwinin, ad d-tger tiɣri i tbezzart di internet akken ad tizmir ad tkemmel i wahil-is n tigawin.
Tirmitin.
D abrid ɣer tifrat n lexsas n waman.
Tesfaydi-d tɣiwant n Tirmitin, yettabaεen ɣer dayra n Draa Ben Khedda, s tullya n yiwet n tɣessart n trumba tagrasent ( station de pompage intermédiaire) n waman tamaynut, yebdan yakan axeddim deg wass n lḥed iεeddan, 28 deg yebrir 2019.
Taɣesart yettwabnan deg umḍiq iwumi qqaren El Kser, i d-yezgan gar tɣessart tadigant 1 n Ubaran d tɣessart tadigant n Hruka, d asenfar i izemren ad d-yejben azal n 150 M3 deg usrag (tsaεett).
Asenfar-agi agejdan, yessefraḥ aṭas imezdaɣ n tɣiwant n Tirmitin, imi ad yekkes fell-asen aɣbel n lexṣas n waman n tissit, ladɣa deg tallit n unebdu.
D ayen, daɣen, ara yessishilen afraq n waman akken iwata lḥal ɣer yimezdaɣ n temḍiqt-agi.
Am wakken ara d-yeglu, diɣ, walluy n tɣessart-agj tamaynut s uneḥbus n usemres n yiqadusen n waman iqburen i icudden ɣer tɣessart n Hruka d Ubaran, i d-yeggran deg yir addad.
Rnu ɣef waya, d ayen ara yessisehlen axeddim ɣef srabes n umesway n Tirmitin d tsemsart n waman.
Ali Zalouk.
At Smaεel.
Asmekti n wass n tmettant n tneglust Ṣunya.
Zerrin tεeddin wussan, akud deg ubrid-is yettazzal, ma d ayen nettidir yal ass, yettuɣal d aktayen, d ismektiyen, gar-asen wid n lεali, wiyaḍ diri-ten.
Am teqṣiḍt n Ṣunya, yiwet n tlemẓit n At Smaεel, i ifernen tamettant ɣef nnif d yiseɣ-is, wala tudert n ddel.
Mraw n yiseggasen i iεeddan yakan ɣef tmettant-is, lameεna ulac win i tt-yettun, ulac win ur nesli s tedyant-is.
Dɣa, ula d wid yellan d imecṭaḥ imir-n, ḥkan-asen yimawlan-nsen tamsalt.
Amek ara tt-ttun yimezdaɣ n taddart n At Smaεel!
Nettat i yuran isem-is deg umezruy s yisekkilen iwṛaɣen, nettat i yellan d azamul n tebɣest, nnif d terbiyya.
D yiwet n tuḥdiqt, tuḥrict, ama deg tɣuṛi-s, ama deg tudert-is.
Ass n 26 di fuṛaṛ 2009, d ass amcum ara yeqqimen d asmekti i yimezdaɣ n At Smaεel s umata.
Ass-n am ussan akk, tekker-d Ṣunya tucbiḥt, truḥ ɣer uɣerbaz i wakken ad tɣeṛ, nettat ur teẓṛi ara belli d win i d ass-is aneggaru di ddunit.
Teɣṛa almi tekfa timsirin-is, teffeɣ-d ahat s lxiq d ccuq ɣer yimawlan-is.
Lameεna, yiwen n uqcic seg twacult-is, yella yettεassa-tt sdat uɣerbaz, imir-n yewwet-itt s ujenwi, yenɣa-tt.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken, aqcic-a ixuṣ deg leεqel, llan wid i d-yeqqaṛen yedderwec, daymi i yexdem ccɣel-a.
Ma yella ɣef tmentilt n tmenɣit-a, d aqcic-a i yellan yettabaε Ṣunya, yessutur-as ad ten-yecrek wassaɣ n tayri.
Aredmani, taqcict taneglust, tuḥṛict, tesεa imir-n ala 15 n yiseggasen, dɣa tugi ad as-teddu di lebɣi, acku d yelli-s n laṣel i tella, d taḥuṛṛit, d tin yefkan azal meqqṛen i tɣuri-s, yerna tegza aṣaḍuf n tudert.
D tidet, Ṣunya temmut, lameεna deg wulawen-nneɣ mazal-itt tedder, acku ayen i texdem ad yili fell-as d anagi i lebda.
Rnu i waya, ad tili d amedya i teqcicin meṛṛa, d akken tin yemmuten ɣef nnif-is, ad tedder i lebda.
Udem gar wudmawen.
42 n yiseggasen segmi d-ilul ugraw Tagrawla.
Ass n 25 yebrir yezrin i d amulli wis 42 segmi d-yella ugraw n ccna amḥaddi “Tagrawla” ass n 25 yebrir 1977, deg tesdawit n tussniwin d tetiknulujit n Bab ẓẓewwar.
D tarbaɛt n semmus n yisdawanen deg tusnakt i t-id-yesnulfan, gar-asen: Idir, Xlifa, Ḥsen, Ḥsisu d Ɛumar.
Syin akkin, sin n yiseggasen seld, yerna-d ɣur-s bu tbatrit Murad Benɛamer, ur nɛeṭṭel deg-s iruḥ.
Deg useggas n 1980, yekcem deg-s Belɛid, deg 1982 yekcem Lwennas, armi d 1984 d Fazil i yernan ɣer terbaɛt.
Yesekles ugraw Tagrawla tasfift tamezwarut deg 1981 deg Paris, ɣer teẓrigin Amina.
Ddant-d deg-s tezlatin yecban « Igujilen », « Afrik » (Taferka), « Nerreẓ », Tiɣri », « Taddart-inu », « Jida », « Tga tiṭ ».
Akken i d-yeqqar yisem-is, yusa-d ugraw Tagrawla akken ad d-yawi amaynut i tmetti, ad yennaɣ s uẓawan, ad yesaki imdanen ɣef tmagit d yidles, am kra n yigrawen n tallit-nni.
Ula d awal-a « tagrawla », nezmer ad d-nini yezga imir-nni deg yilsawen n kra n taggayin n medden i ifaqen, imi ḥsan s temḥeqranit i d-iseɣli umnekcam, i d-iḥettem syin akkin udabu n Lezzayer fell-asen.
Deg yizen n tezlatin n ugraw Tagrawla, aṭas i ikecmen deg uḥric n temḥaddit si tazwara n umecwar-is.
Am tezlit ideg i d-smektayen awal n Masensen « Tafriqt i Yifriqen ».
Neɣ d tin ideg ddmen awal n Si Muḥend Umḥend i yennan « Ad nerreẓ wala ad neknu ».
D waṭas n tezlatin-nniḍen ideg nezmer ad nsel ala i ccna ɣef tlelli n Tmazɣa d Yimaziɣen s umata, akked tegrawla ara igen talast i usehres.
Yewwi-d ad d-nerr awellih ɣef wamek qrib ade temmet taggara-a tezlit tamḥaddit, ma nga aserwes i yiseggasen-nni n 1970, 1980 d 1990.
Merruk.
Arraz i usaru Asaruf n Yunes Budawed.
Tella-d tfaska n usaru amaziɣ n Sinima n Lmerruk ddurt iɛeddan iwumi semman “Tafsut” .
Teḍra-d deg taddart n Tafrut , tedda seg wass n 25 armi d ass n 28 deg yebrir yezrin.
D asiher anda i rran yiɛeggalen-is tajmilt i umsuffeɣ aqbayli n sinima Mass Yunes Budawed , imi i yettekki s usaru ‘Asaruf’ anda i d-yewwi araz mbaɛd imi i d-yettwasenɛet tameddit n wass n 25 yebrir sdat n waṭas n yimferǧen .
Aya, yessefreḥ nezzeh Mass Budawed.
Ɣef waya dɣa, yenna-d i Uɣmis n yimaziɣen : “ Tafaska-agi d ayen yelhan , acku d yiwet n tegnit anda ara tissineḍ wid ixeddmen deg taɣult-agi.
Akken daɣen d tagnit anda i d-nnejmaɛen Yimaziɣen, anda i d-walaɣ kra n tudrin n tmurt-agi.
Ferḥeɣ aṭas imi i yi-xedmen leqdar, ɛerḍen-iyi-d, rran-iyi azal.
Rnu ɣer waya, iɛedda-d usaru n ‘ASARUF’.
Akken daɣen i d-temmeslay tɣamsa tamarukit ɣef wayen i xeddmeɣ, d ayen ara iyi kemmlen afud akken ad rnuɣ deg uxeddim.
Mi ara ak-tuɣal tejmilt di tmurt taberranit, d ayen ara d-yessbegnen belli axeddim-ik, ttwalint wiyaḍ”.
Ma ɣef ssebba i yeǧǧan isura-s ur kkin ara deg tfaskiwin i d-yettilin deg Tizi Uzzu, yessefhem-d : “Di Tizi Uzzu, zgan kkren-iyi-d mgal , axaṭer isura n Budawed, lhan akken iwata.
Ɣer ugdud, nutni ur ḥemmlen ara win ara irebḥen mebla yis- ssen.
Ihi, kkaten akken ad i yi-neṭṭlen , akken ad d-banen kan nutni, acku tetten seg yiwet n tḍebsit”.
Ad d-nesmekti kan belli asaru-agi yettwaheggi-d, ad iɛeddi deg tfaska-nniḍen di temdint n Sus n Merruk di teẓrigt-is tamezwarut .
ayen yessefraḥen, d ayen ara yessuzren ama d tameslay , ama d idles d leɛwayed-nneɣ ɣer wiyaḍ .
Souhila Yamani.
TIZI UZZU - Timlilit ɣef tefsut n tmanyin.
Ansi i d-yekka d wanida i iteddu umennuɣ n umussu !
Yella-d usmekti wis 39 n tefsut n yimaziɣen, ussan n 27 d 28 deg yibrir 2019, s yiwet n temlilit i tga tddukkla Tawacult tagrawlit n lwilaya n Tizi Uzzu deg uxxam n yidles Mulud Mɛemmri n temdin-agi.
Ɣef teɣzi n sin wussan, wwin-d awal yimsaragen ɣef wamek i d-ḍrant tedyanin n tmanyin akked wanda i teddun temsal ass-a n wussan.
Gar wid i yekkan deg usiher-a, ad naf wid i iḥeḍren i tnekkra imir-nni, yecban Lounaouci, Tari Aziz, Yidir Ahmed Zaid, Achab Ramdane, Hebib Youcef, Oussalem Med Ouamar akked kra n wudmawen n umennuɣ ɣef tmaziɣt n tura, am Hakim Saheb, Said Chemakh d Hamou Boumedine.
Deg usarag i d-yefka Ramdane Achab, u uqbel ad d-yawi awal ɣef tedyanin n Tefsut n yimaziɣen, yesmekta-d idlisen i yettwarun ɣef umennuɣ n tmaziɣt s umata, anda i d-yefka dɣa, izwilen n yidlisen-agi, am “Le journal des évenements de 1980”, n Rachid Chaker, “Imaziɣen ass-a” n Salem Chaker, “Chronologie du movement berbère” n Guennon Ali, “ Algérie, citoyenneté et identité” n Brahim Salhi…atg.
“Tadyant n 1980, mačči seg yigenni i d-teɣli, meɛna yella-d umennuɣ ɣef tmaziɣt uqbel yakan.
Llant-d tedyanin uqbel tmanyin i yerfed Umussun aɣelnaw deg yirebbi-s”, i d-yenna Ramdane Achab sdat n waṭas n yimeddukkal-is n umennuɣ s daxel n tzeqqa n Uxxam n yidles Mulud Mɛemmri.
Am wakken i d-iwekked d akken akk timeslayin i yeṭṭfen taqacuct akka tura deg umaḍal, llant akk d tutlayin n yimnekcamen.
Dɣa, ɣef wanect-a, iwala d akken: “Taglizit, tafrensist, taɛrabt neɣ tiyaḍ, d timeslayin n wid yesteɛmren wiyaḍ.
D timeslayin i yettuḥettmen s ddreɛ d zẓur ɣef yigduden i yettwaḥeqqren”.
Uqbel-aya, yenna-d Mass Achab belli awal n tmaziɣt ɣur-s, yerza timeslayin-agi: Taqbaylit, tacawit, tamẓabit, tatergit…atg.
“Ma nniɣ-d Tamaziɣt, meḥsub qessdeɣ-d taqbaylit, tamẓabit, tacawit akked tiyaḍ, mačči kan yiwet n tmeslayt”.
Ma ɣef wayen icerken neɣ yessemgaraden Tafsut n tmanyin akked umussu-agi n tura, walan kra d akken yella wayen i ten-yesdukklen, am wakken i d-yella wayen i ten-yessemxalfen.
Gar wayen i cerken snat n tnekkriwin-agi, d amennuɣ s wudem n talwit.
Ma dayen i ten-iferqen, ad naf d akken amennuɣ n tmanyin, refden-t s umata kra n yiwudam i d-yufraren imir.
Ma d tura, ulac win yettmeslayen s yisem n umussa-agi aɣerfan.
Xas ulamma, mmsefhamen akk ɣef wamek i ilaq ara ikemmel umennuɣ deg unnar, acu kan walan ur yettbeddil ara kra ma yella ur ibeddel ara wudem n tiddin n uwanak.
Hocine Moula.
Wehran.
Asfugel n tefsut n yimaziɣen.
Tiddukkla Numidya n Wehran, ur tezgil ara ttiɛad n usfugel n Tefsut n yimaziɣen deg useggas-is wis 39, imi temmuger aya s yiwen wahil adelsan i d-yeḍran deg Uxxam n tddukkla anda i d-mlalen kra n leqbayel izedɣen deg temnaḍt-a n Wehran akken xersum ad d-smektin ineḍruyen yecban wigi iɣef ruḥen wacḥal d ilmeẓyen d iseflan, akken laṣel d yidles ur neggren ara.
Ɣas ma ameslay s tutlayt-a yenqes sɣur kra n yimezdaɣ n tama-a, tikwal iɣelleb-iten yiles aɛrab, maca mazal llan wid yeṭṭfen di tumast-nsen s tfenṭazit, sselmaden i wid i d-yettenkaren iberdan n tissas s lḥerma d leqder.
Llan-d sin n yisaragen, amezgun akked temsikent.
Ahil n usmekti, tebda-t tddukkla akka;
ass n amhad d sed, tella-d temsikent n yidlisen.
Ass n sed 20 yebrir, nwala-d sin n yisaragen.
Amezwaru yexdem-it uselway n tddukkla Saɛid Zeɛmuc s usentel “Amecwar i d-tezger Tddukkla Numidya seg tuffra ar tallit n wass-a, d umennuɣ i yidra unegmu n tutlayt d yidles amaziɣ deg uɣaram n Wehran”.
Deg-s yuɣal-d ɣer umezruy n tddukkla d wamek i d-tennulfa, tigawin iɣef d-tezger ar ass-a d timmuɣnest n kra seg yiɛeggalen-is ɣas qeṣṣiḥit waṭas n talliyin.
Yerra tajmilt i wid tewwi tmettant, yessaweḍ-asen tamella deg wass n Tefsut n yimaziɣen acku aṭas iqedcen deg urebbi n tddukkla.
Yuɣal-d ɣer ssber n tddukkla-a, yenna-d belli mačči seg yigenni i d-teɣli, acku amer mačči d ssber d limin s leqdic i xeddmen, ur tessawaḍ ara ar 29 n yiseggasen deg tudert-is.
Asarag wis sin, iga-t Mass Karim Ouaras, d aselmad n tefransist di tesdawit n Mestɣanim, yewwi-d asarag-is s usentel “Tazrart ineḍruyen d tedyanin umezruy n umennuɣ i yidra n usṭeɛref s tumast, tutlayt d yidles amaziɣ”.
Anida i yuɣal ɣer useggas n 49, syin i d-zegren leqbayel talliyin s wazal-nsent deg umennuɣ n wass-a s tezɣent tamaziɣt n Ɛimac Ɛmer, Racid Ɛli yeḥya d wiyaḍ.
Syin ikemmel asarag-is ɣef tegnit iɣef d-mlalen ass-a yiɛeggalen d yinebgawen n tddukkla, Tafsut n 80 d tmental i yeǧǧan igiman n yiqbayliyen ad d-ffɣen ɣer ubrid, ad ssutren izerfan-nsen mbeɛd mi yugi udabu n lawan-nni ad d-yili usarag n Dda Lmulud deg tesdawit n Tizi Uzzu.
Yewwi-d daɣen awal ɣef kraḍ n yisuturen igejdanen n Ugraw n Yiɛekkuren deg useggas n 1980.
D Tafsut n 80 i t-yewwin ɣer Tefsut taberkant anda i d-yewwi fell-as awal s telqey d wayen akk d-ssegrant s 127 d ameɣras yeɣlin d luluf n yimejraḥ.
Mi fuken yisaragen, nesla-d i uskasi gar yimeḥḍar d umsarag.
Syin ɣef 18h, nwala-d ayninaw (monologue) n Ḥamid Baḥfir i teɣzi n tsaɛet, yerra iman-is zun d aselway n tegduda ixeṭben agdud-is akken ara yernu yal tikkelt tadwilt tamaynut, uqbel ad yessuref asuter ar taggara deg ugdud-is ɣef tufḍiḥin akk iga, ladɣa timenɣiwt n yilmeẓyen n Tefsut-nni berriken gar-asen Germaḥ Masinisa.
Ma ɣef 19h, llant-d tezlatin n Meɛtub, Ideflawen, Ferḥat d Mengellat i d-cnan sin n yicennayen.
Dagi i ifuk wahil n wass n usfugel wis 39 n Tefsut n yimaziɣen deg Wehran, anida ssarmen yal tikkelt ad d-ttilint tegnatin am ti akken ad d-ttemlilen s leqbayel ad mmeslayen ɣef waddad ideg tella tmaziɣt ass-a d wayen ilaqen akken ad taɣ abrid-is u ad tecbu tutlayin iǧehden n umaḍal.
Khaled Achoui.
Ccmini.
Yeḍra-d ubaxix d ameqqran deg ubrid.
Teḍra-d tasebḥit n wass n, 22 yebrir iɛeddan, yiwet n twaɣit n ubrid d tageɛmirt i yeglan s 6 terwiḥiwin, tesseggra-d s 7 n yimejraḥ.
Yettwajerred waya deg ubrid aɣelnaw wis 26, mi myeẓdamen sin n yikerrusen deg umḍiq iwumi ssawalen « Leɛzib », i yettabaɛen taɣiwant d tdayra n Ccmini.
Ɣef wawal n Uḥuddu aɣarim n Bgayet, i aɣ-d-yuznen ulɣu ass n tedyant gedged, mwaten gar-asen yiwen n usimi akked ukerrus-nniḍen s yisem n Toyota Hilux.
Dɣa, armi d ddurt iɛeddan, yewweḍ leḥsab n wid i tent-yuɣen ɣer 6 n yimattanen i yesɛan gar 18 d 42 n yiseggasen, d 7 n yimejraḥ seg tɣiwant n Msisna, i yesɛan gar 21 d 46 n yiseggasen.
Akken kan leḥqen yirgazen n Uḥuddu aɣarim ɣer wadeg n usehwu-a, sawḍen s tazzla imejraḥ imuḍiren ɣer sbiṭar n Sidi Ɛic.
Ma yella d tifekkiwin yesmiḍen, ttwawint ɣer texxamt n yimattanen n sbiṭar-a daɣen.
Seg tama n leḥsabat n yisehwa n ubrid, seg umenzu n wayyur n yennayer ar 22 deg yebrir 2019 ɣef 10:00, ad d-nselɣu d akken ḍran-d 476 n yisehwa, s 565 n yimejraḥ d 17 n yimattanen.
Am yal tikkelt, yezga yettwessi Uḥuddu aɣarim inehharen akken mačči kan ad ilin d iḥezzaben deg ubrid, maca daɣen d imasayen n tɣellist-nsen d tin n wiyaḍ.
D aya kan i izemren ad d-yawi ugar n talwit deg yiberdan.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken seld tawaɣit-a tageɛmirt, iɛezza Useqqamu aɣerfan awilay n Bgayet (APW) akk tiwaculin n wid yemmuten, deg yiwen n yizen i asent-ibudd.
D tefsut n Yimaziɣen, neɣ n Yiqbayliyen kan ?
Ass n 20 yebrir 2019 i d amulli wis 39 n Tefsut n ttmanyin, wis 18 n Tefsut Taberkant.
D azemz i aɣ-d-yesmektayen ilemẓiyen-nni ileqqaqen i yeɣlin s rrsas n udabu azzayri imi kkren ad sutren tilelli, tugdut d ulmad n tutlayt-nsen deg uɣerbaz.
Kra n yimalasen dɣa send ttiɛad-a n usfuggel d usmekti, aṭas n tamiwin d tddukkliwin i d-yegren tiɣri i tikli di Bgayet, Tizi Uzzu d Tubiret, abeɛda Amussu n ufraniman n Tmurt n Yiqbayliyen.
Maca daɣen, seld aberriḥ-nni mucaɛen n « Xawa-xawa », i d-yeffɣen di tnekkra-a taɣerfant n ugdud azzayri, yella inuḥ usirem ɣur waṭas n yimdanen d kra n yimeɣnasen akken zun ad d-ilint tekliwin-a n usmekti ula deg temnaḍin-nniḍen n Lezzayer.
I wakken xersum ad d-tbin ugar tegmat-a i ttawin ddeqs deg yimawen-nsen.
D acu kan, ayen i aɣ-d-yesken wass n sed 20 yebrir 2019, icuba kan wayen nwala deg yiseggasen iɛeddan, ulamma d amussu n MAK i yeṭṭfen tasga tameqqrant.
Meḥsub, ulac akk win i d-yerran i tiɣri n « xawa-xawa » seg twilayin-nniḍen n Lezzayer ideg ur ssawalen taqbaylit.
Ɣef waya dɣa, ddeqs n yimura, ineɣmasen d yimeɣnasen, i d-yuran deg yiẓeḍwan inmettiyen, mesteqsan ɣef wamek teffeɣ taggara taluft-a.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken llant-d tekliwin di kraḍ n twilayin n tmurt n Yizwawen, ɣas ulamma yella wanida tewɛer tikli neɣ ur wwiḍen yimeɣnasen s amkan di lawan.
Ula d acennay amḥaddi Zedek Mulud, yuɣal-d beddemma si Fransa akken ad yelḥu d ugdud ɣef yiman n yimeɣrasen n Tefsut n ttmanyin d Tefsut taberkant.
Daɣen, i uselɣu, gar wudmawen i yekkin deg tikli, yella uselway aqbur n Ugraw i yidles d tugdut (RCD) Mass Saɛid Seɛdi akked yisegbaren iqdimen n Umussu Adelsan Amaziɣ (MCB).
Ma yella d akabar n FFS ur d-iban, amzun akken ur t-teɛni taluft.
Ɣas ahat llan deg-s yimeɣnasen, maca tasertit n ukabar tḥettem-d abrid-nniḍen taggara-a.
Seld agemmuḍ-nniḍen ideg ala Iqbayliyen i d-yesmektayen tifsutin-a n tnekkra, aṭas i yettmesteqsayen dɣa ma yella ad nessawal i Tefsut n ttmanyin «Tefsut n Yimaziɣen» neɣ «Tefsut n Yiqbayliyen»?
Wehran.
Tella-d temlilit n yiselmaden n tmaziɣt d umaswaḍ-nsen.
Seld mi yekfa amahil-is umaswaḍ n tmaziɣt Mass Abdellah Arkoub deg twilayt n Tlemsan, yerza ɣer yiselmaden n Wehran tazwara n ddurt iɛeddan.
Amahil i t-yewwin ɣer Wehran yemgarad gar usenṣeb n yiwet n tselmadt d tirza n tesweḍt ɣer yiselmaden-nniḍen akked wass n usileɣ i yiselmaden merra n tmaziɣt.
Yebda Mass Ɛerqub leqdic-is ass-nni n acer, 21 yebrir, s tirza ɣer uɣerbaz amenzu Ɛizi Ben Yebqa deg tama n Beṭṭiwa anida i yessenṣeb taselmadt Massa Ǧ.
Smaɛil i yesɣaren yiwet n tnelmadt kan, maca deg uskasi i d-yellan ar taggara gar-as d tnemhalt n uɣerbaz d kra n yimaswaḍen, yenna dakken ilaq ad d-afen tifrat i wugur n tdersi n yinelmaden yeqqaren tamaziɣt deg tneɣriyin, s umeslay d usebɣes n yinelmaden-a, acku ur d-teqqim ara kan deg uselmad, imi aneggaru-a, axeddim-is yettili deg tesmilt s usenked n temsirin.
Deg wass wis sin, arim 22 yebrir, iga umaswaḍ tirza n tesweḍt ɣer sin n yiɣerbazen yellan deg tlemmast n temdint.
Taṣebḥit, yella deg uɣerbaz Ben Tacfin anida i iwala tamsirt n tegnit n tmenna i d-tessenɛet tselmadt ɣef useḥbiber ɣef tdawsa, ma d tameddit yeḥḍer i temsirt deg uɣerbaz El Imam El Hewwari i d-yewwi uselmad ɣef tneqqist n wuccen d yizimer.
Mass Arkoub yumer aṭas s uswir n yinelmaden, acku rran lwelha-nsen akken ilaq ɣer temsirin u ddan d uṣenfar.
Ar taggara, yella-d uskasi gar umaswaḍ d yal aselmad, anida i asen-yefka kra n yiwellihen d lixṣaṣ i iwala ilaq ad yettwixdem, uqbel ad asen-yefk tazmilt ɣef tirza-a.
Ass n arim, d ass n usileɣ deg tesnawit Cellali Xadiǧa deg tama n El Ḥasi, ṣṣbeḥ yewwi-d Mass Arkoub awal ɣef tarrayin iwulmen i uselmed n tmaziɣt ɣer yiɛerbawalen, yefka iwellihen i yiselmaden amek ara ssuddsen asenfar d tgezmin s yiman-nsen war ma smersen adlis aɣurbiz s waṭas, imi d allal ẓẓayen ɣef uswir n yinelmaden-a.
Mbeɛd imekli, uɣalen-d ɣer umahil seg 13h ɣer 15h30, msebḍan yiselmaden ɣef sin n yigrawen, gan amedya n usenfar d tegzemt n waddal n ddabex uḍar s yakk irmuden.
Yumer aṭas umaswaḍ s uswir d unadi xeddmen yiselmaden, ama deg Wehran neɣ di Tlemsan, acku abaɣur d uswir d umḍan n yinelmaden simmal yettnernay, ayagi yakk ahat yezmer ad aɣ-d-yessebgen belli aselmed n tmaziɣt a-t-an deg ubrid iwatan.
D awal-a i swayes i d-yessegra Mass Abdellah mbeɛd mi t-nesteqsa “La teddun lecɣal akken ilaq, ma nwala dakken inelmaden sɛan lebɣi ameqqran i ulmad, ɣas tadra-nsen mačči d leqbayel merra.
Yella daɣen kra n lixṣaṣ yerzan asileɣ imi iselmaden d imaynuten, acu kan s temliliyin am ti simmal yettgerriz waddad”.
Khaled Achoui.
Tiddukkla Oxy-jeunes.
Tikkin deg usileɣ d unebbeh ɣef twennaḍt.
I lmend n usileɣ i d-thegga tddukkla Tiɣri n ugrud n waɣir n Bgayet, tekki tddukkla “Oxy-jeunes” s uselway-is, Mass Xaled Fuḍil akked tselwayt n tseqqamut n tigawt takulujit tasegmant.
Yella-d usileɣ-a seg 19 ar 20 yebrir iɛeddan, ɣef wayen yerzan tigawin i icudden ɣer tmetti d yidles akked umussu asdukklan s umata.
Tga-t-id usileɣ-a, Massa Nur Kawter Huda.
«D akud igerrzen n tmussni, n ulmad, n beṭṭu d tegnit n tegmat (…).
Yella d tadfi d tageɛmirt uzday n usileɣ-a n yimekfaḍuyen akked yimeddukkal isegbaren isdukklanen», i d-yura uselway n tddukkla, Mass Xaled Fuḍil.
Daɣen, tesnemmir tddukkla “Oxy-jeunes” n Yiderginen tamsileɣt d wid yekkin deg usileɣ, am wakken tessayaz (tetthenni) tidukkla timheggit Taɣect n ugrud n Bgayet.
Tettnebbih ɣef temḍerrit n twennaḍt.
Si tama-nniḍen, tettnebbih tdukkla “Oxy-jeunes” n Yiderginen ɣef twaɣit takulujit i d-ibanen di tɣiwant-nsen, i yerzan agudu azayez.
Ɣef wawal n yiɛeggalen n tdukkla-a, ilaq amuqel deg taluft n ugudu-a n lexla, i yellan deg yimi n taddart n Yiderginen, deg ubrid aɣelnaw wis 09.
Imi kra n yimitren kan tama-s, tella din yiwet n tala ansi i tessen yimezdaɣ, aṭas i yebɣan ad yettwakkes ugudu-a, ad yeḥbes dayen uḍegger deg-s.
Daɣen, imi teqreb ɣer udrum n Gar Isaffen, llan azal n 300 n lmitrat kan sɣur-s ar tmiṭ n tɣiwant.
Yettenḍeggar uhicur n ugudu-a deg teẓgi akked wasif Ageryun.
Rnu-as asreɣ i d-yettilin dinna yal ass.
Degmi yella ukukru ad d-derɛen amdan kra n waṭṭanen, ama s ubrid n waman neɣ n nnfu.
Ugar n waya, yettwassen umḍiq-a ula s yibkan, i yellan gar yiɣersiwen yettwaḥudden.
D aya i yeǧǧan ihi iɛeggalen n tddukkla “Oxy-jeunes” ssawalen i wid terza taluft, ad gen kra lawan-a ideg i d-tettqarab tsemhuyt n umerreḥ.
AIT AISSA MIMOUN - Amussu adukklan deg yirebbi n tefsut.
Timlilit n ugraw CRAPES.
Ass-nni n lǧemɛa yezrin 19 yebrir 2019, i d-tella temlilit tamezwarut n umazday n tidmi d tesleḍt tasertant d tdamsant akked tmettit (CRAPES) n tɣiwant n Ait Aissa Mimoun, i d-ilulen ussan-agi kan ineggura.
Agraw-agi, iswi-ines ɣef wakken i t-id-yenna yiwen gar wid i t-id-yesslulen d axlaq n wadeg i umeslay d umbaddal n tiktiwin gar yimdanen.
D annar daɣen i usɣerbel d tesleḍt n wayen yettidir umdan, ama si tama n tsertit ama si tama n tdamsa neɣ si tama n tmetti.
Anejmuɛ-agi amezwaru, yella-d lǧemɛa-agi deffir neɣ deg Tiplakine, yezzi deg-s umeslay s waṭas ɣef yisental-agi igejdanen.
Ad ilin yiswan n tlallit n umazday-agi n yiɣermanen d wahil-is deg wussan i d-iteddun.
Yella-d diɣ umeslay ɣef wazal n teywalt daxel n tmetti, imi ɣef leḥsab n kra txuṣ mliḥ tineggura-a.
Ugar n 30 n yimdanen, gar yisdawanen d yilmeẓyen akked yimussnawen i iḥedren timlilit-agi n tazwara i d-yellan deg unnar.
Imi, niqal amazday-agi yebda-d s yizeḍwa imettiyen (facebook), tuɣal temmeɣ tikti armi i d-ters s annar.
Ma ɣef yiswi agejdan n umazday-agi, yenna-d yiwen gar yimekkiyen n temlilit-a, d axlaq n wadeg n uskasi d tagnit daɣen i ubeddel n tektiwin;
yal wa ad d-yefk tidmi-ines ɣef kra n temsalt ara d-yersen i usqerdec.
Cwiṭ seg tmucuha n leqbayel.
Annar akka i yettwarwat.
Yiwen wass, iwala ugellid n tmurt yelli-s meqqret, yeεni tewweḍ i zzwağ.
Yeqqim yettxemmim weḥd-s, yeqqaṛ: “Ay ul-iw, yelli ṭṭuqten-d fell-as inexḍaben, maca nekk bγiγ-as argaz i tt-yuklalen s tirrugza, mačči s yidrimen”.
Acku yelli-s n ugellid, ur tt-ixuṣ ara uṣurdi, ma textaṛ di kra-nniḍen.
Yettxemmim ugellid armi i t-id-tusa tekti.
Yessawel i kra n yixeddamen-is, yenna-asen: “Ad truḥem ad d-tesnejmaεem meṛṛa At tmurt, ad asen-tinim, agellid yuqqem-d amgarad: win ara ifazen deg-s, ad yawi tarzeft d tameqrant.
Yiwen seg yiqeddacen n ugellid, yenna-as: “Ay agellid, amek ara nini ma steqsan-aγ-d γef ṣṣenf n temsizzelt neγ γef warraz d acut?
”?
Yenna-asen ugellid: “S tidet.
Amgarad d akken win ara yesrewten annar n yirden, ur yumis d aγebbaṛ, d netta ara yaγen yelli tawḥiḍt εzizen”.
Akken i teḍra.
Mi i yeffeγ wawal akk wid-nni i igren iman-nsen deg umgarad, ur zmiren ara acku d awezγi ad tesrewteḍ annar ur tettγebbired.
Armi, a-t-an yekker-d yiwen n yilemẓi, iban yeẓwer, yenna-asen i lεesker n ugellid: “Awit-iyi-d tazart”.
Fkan-as-tt-id, yebda aserwet mebla leḥder am wiyaḍ armi yekfa yuγal ala aγebbaṛ.
Yenna-as ugellid:”Aql-ik ala aγebbaṛ yerna ur teεriḍeḍ ara ad tḥadreḍ iman-ik, d acu i d lmeqsud-ik?
”.
Argaz: “Ay agellid, annar akka i yettwarwat, ma d yelli-k win yebγun, yaγ-itt”.
Yerra-as ugellid: “Ih a mmi d kečč i as-iwulmen”.
Lmeqsud n urgaz d akken ccγel yesεa lqanun, ur yezmir yiwen ad t-ibeddel γef lmeqsud-nniḍen, ama d asurdi ama d ayen-nniḍen, lxudma tettwaxdem akken i as-d-yewwi lḥal.
Qqaṛen wat zik:-“Yir ccγel yettgalla di bab-is”.
Tafsut mm tejmilin.
Fatima Chakour tamɣart mm 117 n yiseggasen.
Ass-nni n lexmis, 25 yebrir 2019, i tuɣal yiwet n tejmilt meqqren sɣur tenmehla n tigawt tinmettit (DAS) n Tizi Uzzu i temɣart tameqqrant akk deg lwilaya n Tizi Uzzu.
Tagi d Fatima Chakour, ilulen s yisem n Khouas.
Tlul deg useggas n 1902, tura ɣur-s lqern d 17 n yiseggasen (117) di leɛmer-is.
Nna Fatima Chakour, mazal-itt ar tizi n wass-a s leɛqel-is, tettnawal i yiman-is.
Ur tesɛi kra n waṭṭan iweɛren, mazal leǧwareḥ-is ṣeḥḥan akken ma ttmallan.
Allaɣ-is d wallen-is ula d iḍarren-is, mazal ǧehden.
Tettidir deg uxxam i d as-yeǧǧa urgaz-is deg taddart n Ighil Bouchene, di tɣiwant n Ait Aissa Mimoun.
Tura akka, ɣur-s ugar n 40 n warraw n warraw-is, i d-rebba s lḥif d lḥifan.
Aṭas n yinebgawen n tenmehla n tigawt tinmettit, i d-yerzan ass-nni n lexmis s axxam-is, am wakken daɣen i iḥedren warraw-is d warraw n warraw-is.
Am wakken yella deg wawal: “Temlal tasa d way turew”.
Nessaram-as teɣzi n leɛmer i Nna Fatima akked tezmert n tzemmurt.
Tafugla i usmekti s Mouloud Yarkal.
Ass-nni n lǧemɛa yezrin 26/04/2019, tella-d tfuglan n usmekti n umerḥum Mouloud Yarkal, i wumi tettuɣal tejmilt s temsizzelt n ddabex uḍar.
Ɣef 8h30 n ssbeḥ, nejmaɛen-d medden d tirni ɣef uẓekka-s, gar yiɛeggalen n twacult-is d yimeddukkal akked yiɛeggalen n ugraw anaddal n Ait Aissa Mimoun, i d-iheggan leqdic-a.
Yella-d usersi n tmeqqunt n yijeǧǧigen ɣef uẓekka-s, syin akkin d ddqiqa n tsussmi.
Am wakken daɣen i d-llant tnagiyin d waktayen n yimeddukkal-is d twcult-is.
Maca, uqbel annect-a, yettili-d ussan-a usiher n waddal, sɣur ugraw n waddal n Ait Aissa Mimoun i gan d tajmilt i umarḥum Yarkal Mouloud, i yellan d ufrin (élu) deg Useqqamu aɣerfan aɣiwan n Ait Aissa Mimoun.
Ass-nni n lǧemɛa, 19 yebrir 2019, i tebda temsizzelt n temliliyin n ddabex uḍar n tɣiwant n Ait Aissa Mimoun, i d-yettilin deg unnar aɣiwan yellan deg Tiplakine.
D timsizzelt n temliliyin, ara yeddun ɣef teɣzi n waṭas n wussan, imi aṭas n temliliyin i yellan.
Mbeɛd mi i d-tella temlilit n tazwara, ass-nni n lǧemɛa iɛeddan ɣef 17h30 n tmeddit gar snat n trebbuyaɛ-agi: Tarbaɛt n taddart n Tahanouts ( taddart n umerḥum-agi) mgal tin n taddart n Ighil Bouchene (taddart n yimsuddsen).
Ttkemmilent temliliyin-agi i d-yettilin yal tameddit n wass ɣef 17h30 n tmeddit deg unnar aɣiwan n Ait Aissa Mimoun.
Yetturaǧu sya ar timlilit n taggara, ara d-yilin ass n lexmis, 09 mayyu 2019, ad d-ilint 14 n temliliyin, sya ar imir.
Ɣer taggara, ad nesmekti belli Mass Yarkal yewweḍ leɛfu Rebbi ass n, 18 yebrir n useggas yezrin, yeǧǧa-d deffir-s sin warraw-is d ilqaqen.
Cwiṭ seg tmucuha n leqbayel.
Annar akka i yettwarwat.
