Yahia Yanes.
Taseqqamut tadigant n Yitri azeggaɣ azzayri n Mεatqa.
Ihegga-d yiwet n temhelt n ṭṭhara.
I lmend n wass n 27 seg waggur n Remḍan 2019, thegga-d Teseqqamut tadigant n Yitri azeggaɣ azzayri n Mεatqa yiwet n temhelt n ṭṭhara i lfayda n yigerdan n twaculin yenḥafen n tɣiwant n Mεatqa akked tɣiwant n Ssuq El Tenin.
Ajered i twaculin i yebɣan ad sḍehrent i yigerdan-nsent, ad d-yili seg umenzu (1) ɣer 4 seg waggur n maggu 2019, deg tebda n teseqqamut i d-yezgan deg yidigan n tɣiwant n Mεatqa, seg 10 n tsebḥit ar 17 n tmeddit.
Akken tuɣ tannumi teseqqamut tadigant n Yitri azeggaɣ azzayri n Mεatqa s tigawin-is n lxir i lfayda n yimezdaɣ n temḍiqt-agi, dɣa, ayen yakk yeεnan tamhelt-agi, ad d-yili s lmendad n teseqqamut d tallelt n yimdanen yenwan lxir, ama d lebsa, d dwawi akked tmeɣra ara d-yilin deg yiḍ n wass n temhelt i twaculin n yimeḍharen.
Tamkerḍit n ubrid.
Sdat n umyezwar ɣer wumḍiq amzwaru deg temsizzelt n taddart tazeddgant deg ugerzu n Tizi Uzzu, i d-yessuddes Useqqamu aɣerfan n ugerzu, yal taddart, tettnadi ad d-tufrar ɣef tayeḍ s tigawin d leqdicat yemgaraden.
S leqdicat ara yefken udem igerrzen i taddart u ara wa iwenεen tudert n yimezdaɣ n yal ass akked wayen ara yezdin tagmat gar yimezdaɣ n tudrin.
Dɣa akka i d-tufrar tɣiwant n Mεatqa s yiwen n leqdic igerrzen nezzeh, i d-yellan i tikkelt tamezwarut deg temḍiqt-agi n leqbayel.
Aya, dayen yeεnan alluy n yiwet n temkerḍit n ubrid yezdin yakk imezdaɣ.
Tikti-agi, tella-d s ɣur n tddukkla tadelsant n Tiɣilt n Teqḍibin, yettabaεen ɣer taddart n Ibarquqen.
Teldi temkarḍit-agi deg tlemmast n taddart ɣer rrif n ubrid, s ddaw n usentel “ Ddem adlis, teǧǧeḍ-d adlis”.
Leqdic yecban wa, dayen ara d-ixelqen tayri n tɣuri gar leǧiran d yimezdaɣ n taddart.
Rnu ɣef waya, ad yili lḥir meqqren ɣer yilmeẓyen deg unadi ɣef tumussniwin yemgaraden.
Am waken neẓra, tussna ad d-teglu s yidles n taẓunt, s wacu ara bnun yimdanen tawejiḍt ireẓnen iman-is.
Ait Aissa Mimoun.
Aheggi i ṭṭhara n yigerdan yenxeṣṣen.
Mi ara d-yeqreb waggur n Remḍan, ṭṭuqutent tigawin n temsetla (lemɛawna) gar yimdanen.
Dɣa di ddurt-agi kan iɛeddan, i d-iger Waggur azeggaɣ azzayri n tama n Ait Aissa Mimoun s tallelt n tddukkla tadelsant Imnar n Tdukli, yiwet n teɣri i yimezdaɣ n tɣiwant-agi i wakken ad jerden igerdan-nsen ara d-izeynen.
ebda ujerred ass-nni n lexmis, 25 deg waggur-agi n yebrir, yetturaǧu ad yessali ass n tsewwiqt n Remḍan, ara d-yilin ass n, 5 deg waggur n maggu 2019.
Yettili-d ujerred n yigerdan yenxeṣṣen, yenwan ad ḍehren aseggas-a, sɣur n Aggur azeggaɣ azzayri n Ait Aissa Mimoun, yellan deg taddart n Tahanouts.
Yetturaǧu ad yili uzyen-nsen deg tɛecret taneggarut n waggur n Remḍan, imi mazal ur iban ara wazemz unṣib n ṭṭhara-agi.
D imsuddsen n leqdic-agi ara d-yelhin s yigerdan-agi segmi ara tebdu temhalt-agi alamma tekfa.
Bdu-tt-id s tuqqna n lḥenni d uselsi n yiselsa n umeḍhar alamma dayen ḍehren-d.
Uqbel tamhalt-agi n ṭṭhara, yetturaǧu ad tili tfugla neɣ tmeɣra ɣef lmendad n yimedharen-agi.
Yezmer lḥal ad tili uqbel ad zeynen s yiwwas neɣ s sin wussan kan.
Ma d ahil n tmeɣra-a, ɣef wakken i t-id-nnan yimsuddsen-agi, ad yili d anesbaɣur i lfayda n twaculin n yimedharen-agi.
Gar ccna, taḍsa akked unecreḥ, tuqqna n lḥenni, tibuɣrain…atg.
er taggara, ad d-nesmekti kan belli, imsuddsen-agi bdan ajmeɛ n yidrimen swayes ara qablen tamhalt-agi n ṭṭhara n yigerdan yenxeṣṣen.
Am wakken daɣen i yetturaǧu ad ilin leqdicat-nniḍen sya ɣer sdat, gar sin-agi n yimsuddsen.
Ghani Amazigh.
Yella-d usmekti n Tefsutin deg Uweqqas.
I lmend n usmekti n Tefsut n yimaziɣen akked Tesfut taberkant, thegga-d tddukkla Izeɣmar Taremant n Uweqqas i wass n 19 yebrir ahil i yebdan ɣef 13h s yiwet n temsikent ɣef tedyanin i d-yeḍran di temnaḍt n leqbayel.
Syin, llan-d sin n yisaragen ɣef tedyain-agi.
Amezwaru sɣur Mass Chabane Mourad akked Mass Aidali Hamou, wis sin d asqerdec ɣef tmagit sɣur iselmaden n tmaziɣt, Mass Ayad Salim, Massa Aissou Ourida , akked umedyaz Mass Hebbache Yacine.
Am wakken i d-tettunefk tegnit diɣ i ccna amḥaddi sɣur icennayen Lahlou Kamel, Djouadi Aziz, Mouzaoui Mouloud akked uḥric i tmedyazt sɣur Mass Douadi Akli.
Deg taggara, walan yimdanen i d-yerzan ɣer din tamezgunt “Amejmaj” i d-iqeddem Mass Bellouz Nadir.
S wakka, ihi, i ssulin yiɛeggalen leqdic-nsen i lmend n usmekti n uzemz-agi i ireṣṣan deg wallaɣ n yal Aqbayli, neɣ Amaziɣ s umata.
Yamani Souhila.
Sṭif.
Kra n yisufar n wučči, ḍḥan-d d amihi ɣef warrac.
Yewwi-d ɣef yibabaten n warrac, ad rren awellih-nsen nezzeh i wayen i d-ttaɣen dderya-nsen deg berra, acku aqcic amectuḥ ur yeẓri ara d acu i d učči i as-ilaqen.
Rnu i waya, llan wid ur nessin ad d-ɣṛen azemz n tmettant n wučči-nni.
Dɣa, d ayen i yeḍṛan di twilayt n Tbeskert (Bisekra), anda i yuzzlen aṭaṣ n yimezdaɣ i uccekti ɣef yiwet n tkebbanit n Ṣṭif, i ixeddmen iẓmi n warrac imectaḥ, asafar-a isem-is  » Yupi « .
Ayen yessewhamen deg temsalt-a, imi ufan wid i d-yuɣen asafar-a, azemz wis sin s ufella, yeffer win idetti s wadda.
Dɣa iẓmi-a, yettwaxdem di 3/2017, ad yemmet di 9/2018.
Lameεna uran s ufella-s belli yettwaxdem di 06/2018, wa ad yemmet di 12/2019.
Ihi wid i t-id-yuɣen swan iẓmi yexṣeṛ.
Seg tama-s tanmehla n ttjaṛa, teldi anadi ɣef usentel-a amihan.
Daymi, i ilaq yal yiwen deg-neɣ ad yettḥadar iman-is.
Imi tekfa telsawit deg wulawen, yesderɣel udrim imdanen.
Xeṛṛaṭa.
Yettwasbedd uselway amaynut n tɣiwant.
Am twilayin akk n Lezzayer, teṭṭef tsertit amdiq-is deg tudert n yal ass n yimdanen, ladɣa segmi i d-yekker ugdud.
Dɣa, am win yellan yakan yettabeε-itt, am win yexḍan seg-s, uɣalen akk medden d isertanen.
D aya i yeḍṛan di tɣiwant n Xeṛṛaṭa, imi yeṭṭuqet umeslay ussan yezrin ɣef liḥala i tettidir tɣiwant-a.
Ladɣa segmi i yeṭṭaxeṛ Saεid Ḥamamin i yellan d aselway n tɣiwant-a seg umḍiq-is ass n ,31 di meɣṛes 2019.
Seld aya, imḍebbṛen n tɣiwant-a, akked wid teεna temsalt nnejmaεen i wakken ad d-afen tifrat i temsalt-a.
Dɣa, akken i d-yeqqaṛ uṣaḍuf, ma yella iṛuḥ uselway n tɣiwant, d yiwen seg urbaε-is ara yeṭṭfen amkan-is.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken, agraw-nsen d agraw n yilelliyen, rnu i waya, d nutni i yesεan ugar n tuɣac.
Γef waya i sbedden Mass Fennuc Reḍwan deg umkan n uselway aqbuṛ.
Ayagi, yella-d deg uxxam n tɣiwant, sɣuṛ uselway n tdayṛa, i d-yusan deg umkan n lwali, d yixeddamen n tɣiwant, akked yimezdaɣ-is.
Ɣef leḥsab n teɣbalut-nneɣ, aselway-a amaynut, yefka-sen awal i yimezdaɣ belli ad yexdem nnig n tezmert-is i ubaɣuṛ n tuddar n tɣiwant meṛṛa.
Yerna ad yeεṛeḍ ad iqeεεed ayen deg wacu ideg xuṣṣent seg yal tama, ama d tin n waman n tissit d tdamsa s umata, neɣ d tin n usegmi d tiyaḍ.
Lameεna ayagi, ɣef leḥsab-is, ad d-yili s ufus n tallelt n at tuddar d lebɣi-nsen i ubeddel.
Ajdid di tira.
Iles, times d amaynut n Muḥemmed Ḥaǧimi.
Deg wussan-agi kan iɛeddan, i d-yeffeɣ ɣer ssuq udlis wis tlata n umaru d umedyaz Muḥemmed Ḥaǧimi, iwummi isemma Iles, times.
D ammud n tmedyazt wis kraḍ, i d-yessuffeɣ ɣer tezrigin n Ccix Muḥend Ulḥusin n Tizi Uzzu.
Yettnuzu s wazal n 150 DA.
D taselmadt n tmaziɣt Belḥusin Nasiṛa, i d as-yerran tazwert n udlis-agi n 48 n yisebtar.
D ammud n tmedyazt, ideg ara naf 21 d asefru s teqbaylit timserreḥt, yeččuren d sser d ccbaḥa akked wawal aziḍan.
Yettleqqim tamussni-s deg yisefra s wawalen iqburen, yessefruy s teqbaylit-nni taqurant.
Ma d isental iɣef i d-yewwi awal deg wammud-agi, mačči yiwen, mačči sin, gten.
Tuget n yisefra-s, tezzin ɣef tnagit n tegrawla tazzayrit (Awal n umeɣras), tamagit d yidles amaziɣ (Asmekti n tefsut), tayri (Tayri ifuḥen, Tajeǧǧigt n ddunit, Ansayen n tayri)…atg.
Nger tamawt deg yisefra-agi, nufa-d belli Mass Ḥaǧimi, yessefray s 6 n yifyar i yal taseddart, ma tameɣurt i d-yettuɣalen deg yisefra-a d AB/AB/AB.
Ad d-nesmekti kan belli, Mass Ḥaǧimi Muḥemmed, d amedyaz d amaru.
Yettales-d diɣ timucuha i warrac, am wakken diɣ i yettaru timezgunin sya ɣer da.
D argaz bu tebɣest meqqren, ulamma 79 n yiseggasen di leɛmer-is maca mazal deg-s ifadden d leḥrara n uxeddim ɣef yidles d tutlayt tamaziɣt.
Ilul ass n 15 deg cutember 1941 deg taddart n Cender deg tɣiwant n Naṣirya deg lwilaya n Bumerdas.
Udem gar wudmawen.
Zrin 7 n yiseggasen ɣef tmettant n ucennay Mhenni.
Tettuɣal-d Tefsut n yimaziɣen s lfuruḥ d tmeɣriwin yal mi ara d-tezzi.
Ɣef teɣzi n mraw n wussan ineggura n yebrir, ttilin-d leqdicat idelsanen yemxalafen;
tuget d wid i d-ssuddusent tddukkliwin tidelsanin.
20 yebrir, daɣen, d yiwen n wazemz i d-yettuɣalen s waktay-nniḍen, imi ass-nni i aɣ-yeǧǧa yiwen wudem n ccna d ssinima n teqbaylit zeddigen.
Wagi d acennay Amroun Mhenni i tewwi tmettant deg wass n 20 yebrir 2012.
Ɛemrun Mhenni, d anaẓur aqdim.
Ilul ass n 3 duǧember 1938 deg Buzgan.
Seg temẓi-s i yebda ccna, mi akken iḥeffeḍ s wul tizlatin n Sliman Ɛazem.
Uqbel ad tekker tegrawla n Lezzayer, iruḥ ɣer tmurt n Fransa, yekki di tfidiralit n FLN deg temdint n Marseille.
Mi d-yuɣal ɣer tmurt seld tagrawla, yekcem ɣer rradyu, din i yexdem geddac n tceqqufin n umezgun akked wudmawen yettwassnnen deg umezgun n teqbaylit.
Ma nuɣal-d ɣer ssinima, yekki deg waṭas n yisura yesɛan inumak lqayen n tmetti d wayen icudden ɣur-s, gar-asen Aḥlil aḥli, Axxam n Dda Meẓyan… Ma d ccna, ad naf gar tezlatin yettwassnen i d-yeǧǧa Mhenni Ɛemrun, ad d-nebder deg-sent Tettcekkireḍ-iyi-d jeddi-k, A jeǧǧiga.
Tasdawit Mulud MƐemmri Seg usarag ɣer usarag-nnḍen.
Yal askasi s yinebgawen-is.
Segmi yebda umussu-agi aɣerfan, i d-yebdan ass n lǧemɛa 22 yebrir 2019, tekcem tmurt deg yiwet n tallit tamxaleft deg umezruy n tmurt n Lezzayer.
Mbeɛd mi yenqes s waṭas leqdic adelsan deg tesdawit n Tizi Uzzu, ladɣa deg wayen yerzan isaragen d temliliyin n yimussnawen n yal taɣult.
Yedda-d yid-s ubeddel n tmuɣliwin n tikta i d-ilulen d timaynutin, ideg yesɛa asirem ugdud azzayri.
Lqid yettwakkes, abrid iregglen dayen yenǧer, ula d asalu yuɣal yessen abrid-is.
Uɣalent-d tmeqwa ɣer tregwa, dayen i d-yerran leqdic ussnan d udelsan ɣer tesdawit n Tizi Uzzu.
Yal ddurt, s yisaragen-is d temliliyin-is akked yinebgawen i d-yettawin awal ɣef geddac n yisental.
Bdu-tt-id seg usarag n mass Said Khelil, i d-yellan ass-nni n lexmis 21 meɣres 2019 deg tesdawit n Mulud Mɛemmeri alamma tleḥqeḍ-d ɣer yisaragen ddurt iɛeddan, anda i d-tella temlilit n tlata n yimussnawen-agi: Hocine Zehouane, Nasreddine Lezzar akked Arezki Lakabi, ass-nni n larebɛa 17 yebrir 2019, anida i d-mmeslayen ɣef tezɣent tamirant ideg tettidir ass-a tmurt n Lezzayer, d acu n tifrat i izemren ad tili sya ɣer sdat.
Awal ad t-id-nawi ɣef usarag aneggaru n ddurt iɛeddan, i d-yellan ass-nni n lexmis 18 yebrir 2019, ideg yella Uduktur Said Sadi d inebgi n usarag aneggaru n ddurt yezrin.
Limmer si 62 i tefra, tili ass-a mačči akka !
Di tazwara n usarag yemmeslay-d ɣef tesfut taberkant yenna-d : “Uqbel ad bduɣ asarag, bɣiɣ ad d-iniɣ sin yimeslayen ɣef wigi i d-ileqmen ameslay di tesdawit-agi anda nella , imi syagi i tebda taluft’’.
Yemmeslay-d ɣef wamek i d-tebda tefsut taberkant, d wamek i d as-ugin i Mulud Mɛemmri akken ad yexdem asarag-is.
Syin ɣers, yenna-d belli “d tafsut n yiḍelli i d-yewwin tagi n wass-a”, yerna-d deg wawal-is : “Ilaq di teswiɛd am tagi yal yiwen ad yerr di lbal-is belli : “Armi d ass-a i d-tlul tmurt n Lezzayer.
Tamsalt yecban tagi, mačči d ayen ara iqabel umdan weḥd-s , mačči d ayen ara yefru ukabar weḥd-s”.
Akken daɣen i yexdem amgarad gar umennuɣ n zik akked win n tura, ɣef waya iwekkded belli zik asmi i ttnaɣen, ur yelli ara d amennuɣ n talwit am wass-a ,yerna-d : “Akuffer-nni id aɣ-yeṭṭfen asmi igedlen i Mɛemmri asarag, yettak acbi ɣef ukuffer-agi n wass-a imi i d ak-d-nnan : “Ad nesbedd Lkadr akken ad yeḥkem fell-awen i lebda”.
Gar wayen i d yenna : “Limer tebna ddewla n Lezzayer di 62 ɣef wakken i tt-ḥwaǧen yimdanen, ɣef wakken i d-yella umezruy n tmurt, ɣef wakken i nettwali tameddurt-nneɣ, tili ass-a ur nettili ara di tugnit anida ur telli ddewla, ur yelli lḥeqq, ur telli tidet.
Si 62, ddwla tebda s ddraɛ, tekfa s ddraɛ”.
Ifures tagnit akken ad yini i yilmeẓyen i yellan s tuget deg usarag, d akken tura “ilaq ad nessers lsas n tigduda, ilaq anegzu akken ilaq ayen i iḍerrun akken ad nwali amek ara nkemmel” .
Akken daɣen i d-yewwi awal ɣef yimeslayen i d-yeffɣen taggara-agi belli annay amaziɣ yettwagdel deg tmanaɣt yenna-d : “Annay amaziɣ d yiwen n uzamul i yeɛnan yakk Tafriqt n Ugafa , ilaq ad fehmen anect-agi”.
Akken daɣen ur yezgil ara ayen i d-yeḍran taggara-agi mgal tulawin imi i d-yewwi awal ɣef utekki n tmeṭṭut deg tnekriwin-agi, yenna-d belli “tajmilt tameqqrant ad as-tuɣal i tmeṭṭut imi tella-d di tikliwin-agi , maca akken twalam yakk d akken llan wid iwumi ur yeɛǧib ara lḥal”.
Yemmeslay-d daɣen ɣef yizerfan n tmeṭṭut .
“Ay ilmeẓyen aqli-ken tettidiren yiwen n tallit d tamxalleft.
Ilaq ad teẓrem ayen ara d-iḍerrun, ur ilaq ara ad aɣ-kellxen.
Ilaq iɣeblan, ad rsen tura di tallit-agi n ubeddel , gar-asen : Tugdut, aseɛdel gar urgaz d tmeṭṭut , aqader n ugdud , syin ɣer-s ad ilint tefranin”.
Syin, yettunefk wawal i wid yebɣan ad steqqsin Mass Saɛid Saɛdi.
Aṭas n yisteqsiyen i d-yellan ladɣa seg yilmeẓyen.
D ayen i yessefraḥen, acku d nutni i d azekka n tmurt, d nutni i ilaq ad issinen tasertit akken ad sɛun s wayes ara qablen taswiɛt , maca nexdem tamawt d akken ulac aṭas n tulawin i d yellan deg usarag d timexḍa , d ayen i yesḥissifen, acku tameṭṭut ass-a, yewwi-d fell-as akken ad tessekcem iman-is deg yal taɣult .
Iḍelli n lḥed 21 yebrir 2019, yella-d usarag amcarek amezwru n ddurt-agi, ideg i d-yemlal Oussalem Mohand Ouamer, Remdane Achab akked Salah Oudahar.
Deg tlata yid-sen mmeslayen-d ɣef yimal n tmaziɣt deg Tegduda tamezwarut n tmurt n Lezzayer, i izemren ad tlal sya d afella.
Am wakken daɣen yetturaǧu, ad d-yili usarag i ttraǧun yisdawanen s ccuq, wagi d win ara d-yawi Mass Mustapha Bouchachi.
Yetturaǧu ad d-yili ass n larebɛa-agi sdat-nneɣ, ad d-yemmeslay deg-s ɣef usentel “Acu-tent tifratin tisertanin n tezɣent ideg tettidir tmurt n Lezzayer tineggura-a?
